																
Project 002A																
			Powerbus starts at index 0													
			simple led with 2 switches in parallel													
																
FROM arduino																
																
5 volt (red wire)						POWERBUS 0 → 0st Positive connection										
Ardunio GROUND						POWERBUS 0 → 1st Negative connection										
																
																
breadboard 																
																
POWERBUS						PROTO AREA										
																
PB1	1	positive		--->		8A	Resistor									
																
						SWITCH   UNIT A										
						TOP LEFT			8E							
						TOP RIGHT			8F							
						BOT LEFT			10E							
						BOT RIGHT			10F							
																
						SWITCH   UNIT B										
						TOP LEFT			12E							
						TOP RIGHT			12F							
						BOT LEFT			14E							
						BOT RIGHT			14F							
																
						First shared connection 										
						8B to 12B										
																
						2nd shared connect										
						14B to 20B										
																
						10A to 20A										
																
																
						Connection from switch to led power										
						10D	to 	13D								
																
						LED RED										
						Anode long side				20E						
										21E						
																
						Connection from LED to ground helper wire										
PB2	1	to negative				21A										
																
